data.description: Three bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 3 car garage  on 5 acres. Multiple sheds included. On its own well & Septic. Completely secluded.  Mature trees throughout the property .  This property has so much potential .  Keep the front house as a mother’s quarters and build your dream home in the back.  Hóme is on propane. This would also be a phenomenal flip!  More pictures to come this week on the interior.
